      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six pulls linearly to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and proactive rod bearing replacement. The 6-speed manual transmission delivers crisp, tactile shifts, while the chassis remains taut thanks to a reinforced rear subframe and fresh bushings. Finished in its original factory paint with a flawless interior, this vehicle retains its factory-spec geometry and mechanical integrity. A turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
